---
title: Double Indian Chicken & Roast Pumpkin Curry with Baby Leaves & Jasmine Rice
description: This fluffy rice needs to soak up the ultimate curry, so we present to you just that! A creamy yet spiced curry with two spice blend powerhouses, the Mumbai and mild North Indian spice blend. Add the chicken and pumpkin and you’re ready to dig in as soon as this curry is served.
